### Good Hamburger API — Testes Manuais
### Use a extensão "REST Client" do VS Code para executar estes requests.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiKey = goodhamburger-local-dev-key
@orderId = {{createOrder.response.body.$.id}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CARDÁPIO
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### GET — Listar cardápio completo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/menu
Accept: application/json

###

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PEDIDOS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### POST — Criar pedido (combo completo → 20% desconto)
# @name createOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [1, 4, 5]
}

###

### POST — Criar pedido (sanduíche + bebida → 15% desconto)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [2, 5]
}

###

### POST — Criar pedido (sanduíche + batata → 10% desconto)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [3, 4]
}

###

### POST — Erro: dois sanduíches (deve retornar 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [1, 2]
}

###

### POST — Erro: item inexistente (deve retornar 404)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [999]
}

###

### POST — Erro: lista vazia (deve retornar 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": []
}

###

### GET — Listar todos os pedidos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### GET — Buscar pedido por ID (substitua o GUID abaixo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### GET — Pedido inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/ffffffff-ffff-ffff-ffff-ffffffffffff
Accept: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###

### PUT — Atualizar pedido (substitua o GUID abaixo)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "menuItemIds": [1, 4, 5]
}

###

### DELETE — Remover pedido (substitua o GUID abaixo)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

###
